Specific style asks:

1. No throat-clearing introductions. The recommendation is paragraph one.
2. Every option section has the same sub-headings, in the same order, every time.
3. Tables for anything comparative — never prose comparisons across 3+ options.
4. Confidence labels (High / Medium / Low) on any claim that isn't directly sourced.

